lead_paragraph: Super Bowl MVP Von Miller etched his place in NFL history but on Monday was full of praise for Peyton Manning, saying the Denver Broncos' triumph was about much more than just his dominant defensive effort.

headline.print_headline: Super Bowl MVP Miller Credits Peyton, Coaches for Win
